latestIgtvVideos.title: The BEST Dry Shampoo EVER
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
If you are looking for a new dry shampoo... look no further!

I’ve been testing the new @designmehair dry shampoo for a while now and love it! [a.d.]

Their new packaging is perfect for the spring/summer (and BEACH🏝) and smells like fresh citrus & fruits. It doesn’t leave any white spots in your hair, and keeps your hair fresh for days to come.

Definitely recommend checking it out! 

What are your summer plans?! Let me know!👇🏻💗✨
